spec_data.Name: compat-glibc
spec_data.License: LGPLv2+ and LGPLv2+ with exceptions and GPLv2+
spec_data.Description:
This package contains stub shared libraries and static libraries
from Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6.

To compile and link against these compatibility libraries, use
gcc -fgnu89-inline \
      -I /usr/lib/x86_64-redhat-linux6E/include \
      -B /usr/lib/x86_64-redhat-linux6E/lib64/
